Both operations happen in a single transaction for undo atomicity.

Accepts the same simple or full config formats as `add()`.
@param - Name for the new sheet
@param - Pivot table configuration
@param - Creation lifecycle; defaults to defineOnly.
@returns A receipt containing the new sheet ID and created pivot config.

